  EffectDiscription_ENG: Your [Lucemon] can digivolve into this card in your hand
    for a memory cost of 7, ignoring this card's digivolution requirements. For every
    10 cards in your trash, reduce the memory cost when playing this card from your
    hand by 3. [On Play][When Digivolving] Delete 1 of your opponent's Tamers or
    level 6 or lower Digimon.
